Reference authoritative sources: Fennema's Food Chemistry (Damodaran et al., 5th ed.), Belitz et al. Food Chemistry (4th ed.), BeMiller Carbohydrate Chemistry, Roos Phase Transitions in Foods, Phillips & Williams Handbook of Hydrocolloids, MacDougall Colour in Food.

